						<p>On a slab set up at the entrance of a cavern in the village.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 1754, Khara, Jyēshṭha ba 7, Saturday.</p>						

						<p>Records the installation of image Ōṅkārēśvara in the cavern <hi rend="italic">(bilagarbha)</hi> at Guttikoṇḍa on this day.</p>						

