<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrī svasti śrī jayābhyu 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>daya śālivāhana śakā 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>bdaṁbulu 1754 <g type="ddanda">.</g> Agunē 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṭi kharanāma saṁvatsara jē 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṣṭa bahuḷa saptamī śu 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>bhadina stiravāraṁ gutti 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>koṁḍa bilagarbhamaṁduna 
<lb n="8"/>Ōṁkārēśvara svāmi vāri 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ni pratiṣṭa cēśina sumuhū 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>rtaṁ <g type="ddanda">.</g> śrīśrīṁ jēyu 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>nū <g type="ddanda">.</g> 
</p>

